      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCb0522a882b24100585a8c6c5c869a9d2"></a>Refitting the hand guards
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e5874"> </a>If disassembled, reassemble hand guards following the disassembly procedure in reverse order. Remember to tighten screws (8)
            to 0.45 Nm ± 10%.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_014003261.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e5879"> </a>Refitting the hand guards is the reverse of removal, tighten the screw (3) to a torque of 2 Nm ±10% and the screws (2) to
            a torque of 5 Nm ±10%.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e5881"> </a>Tighten screw (6) to a torque of 10 Nm ±10%. 
         </div>
      </div>
